step 1: Go to Folder C:\php-0.0.20
step 2: Copy and paste php.ini-development
step 3: Rename php.ini-development ➡️ php.ini
step 4: Open php.ini
step 5: Uncomment extension=mysqli
                  extension=pdo_mysql
                  extension_dir = "ext"
step 6: change path to extension_dir = "C:\php-8.4.2\ext"
step 7: run in terminal php -S localhost:8000
step 8: http://localhost:8000/sample.html